  <div class="content" style="margin: 10px auto;">
    <p>Managing payroll for your business can be a time-consuming process. At American Payroll Services, Inc.,
(APS), we handle your payroll administration needs, leaving you with more time to do what you do best
- <b>run and grow your business!</b> APS ensures that your payroll needs are met on time, helping you to
streamline your payroll process, improve productivity and simplify administration. APS has been
featured in Forbes, June 2007, <a href="/rocket-software-prevents-data-theft-with-securityvault-enterprise-edition.html" class="fbox" rel="nofollow">Click Here</a> to see the article.</p>
<h2>Why APS?</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Flexible, accurate, and accountable</li>
  <li>Dedicated payroll experts</li>
  <li>All 50 states covered</li>
  <li>Coverage tailored to your field</li>
  <li>Guaranteed savings over large payroll bureaus</li>
</ul>
<p>APS makes sure your checks are properly processed and delivered on time and that your data is always
secure. Services include comprehensive Client Portal setup and training.</p>
